ption><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 23:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-trying-but-pinning-gaza-debacle-on-the-defense-establishment-wont-be-easy/0000018b-da6c-d168-a3ef-dffebe3d0000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官：哈马斯将失去加沙，红十字会必须进入以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/top-european-diplomat-hamas-will-lose-gaza-red-cross-must-get-access-to-israeli-hostages/0000018b-d9db-df9a-ab8b-dfdbace10000</link><description>欧盟外交部长何塞普·博雷尔表示，必须释放哈马斯扣押的所有人质，并呼吁以色列表现出更多克制，并接受在战斗中延长人道主义暂停时间的想法</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 23:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/top-european-diplomat-hamas-will-lose-gaza-red-cross-must-get-access-to-israeli-hostages/0000018b-d9db-df9a-ab8b-dfdbace10000</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员如何在以色列和加沙问题上达成民主党和犹太人的共识</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/how-a-u-s-senator-captured-the-democratic-and-jewish-center-on-israel-and-gaza/0000018b-da25-d168-a3ef-dfffb4140000</link><description>来自格鲁吉亚的犹太参议员乔恩·奥索夫 (Jon Ossoff) 连贯、清晰地表达了三个可以共存的想法：哈马斯的袭击显然是错误的，以色列有权以武力回应以保护自己，加沙无辜的巴勒斯坦平民应该受到惩罚。保护</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 22:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/how-a-u-s-senator-captured-the-democratic-and-jewish-center-on-israel-and-gaza/0000018b-da25-d168-a3ef-dfffb4140000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加被杀的加拿大以色列和平活动家维维安·西尔弗的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-funeral-of-slain-canadian-israeli-peace-activist-vivian-silver/0000018b-d9cd-d423-affb-fbef6e360000</link><description>以色列社会各界人士前来向西尔弗告别，西尔弗于 10 月 7 日在贝埃里基布兹的家中被哈马斯杀害。“你知道，我们说希伯来语还是阿拉伯语并不重要，这并不重要。”无论我们是出生在加沙边境还是加沙地带，你都知道我们的未来是紧密相连的。”和平活动家加迪尔·哈尼 (Ghadir Hani) 说道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 21:38:32 